title: Barca Beat The Registration Race
description:
The FC crew react to Barcelona finally being able to register a majority of their new signings on the evening of their opening LaLiga match and question if Jules Kounde will be registered in time. Plus, the guys preview this weekend's London Derby and argue if Spurs have caught up to Chelsea this offseason.
